data.description: **3.25% interest rate assumable FHA mortgage AND a $10,500 price reduction** Step into the charm of this exquisite 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom bungalow nestled in the heart of Tooele, Utah! A perfect fusion of timeless elegance and modern comfort, this home offers a #BETTERTHANEXPECTED living experience.  From the friendliest of neighbors to the concerts in the park near by, and only steps away from nearby schools this home location is most desirable!   Imagine hosting social events in the spacious living areas and the semi formal dining room, adorned with tasteful decor that complements your personal style.  Escape to the cozy bedrooms, each promising restful nights, and wake up to the warm Utah sun streaming through the windows. The rooms and bathrooms boast a touch of modern delight, ensuring both convenience and indulgence.   Wrap up next to the fireplace this holiday season with some cocoa and let's make your home ownership desires a reality with this delightfully quaint home. Schedule your tour soon!
